com.ibm.mq.explorer.ms0s.mqsceditor.gui

Class MQSCContentOutlinePage

  • java.lang.Object
    • ContentOutlinePage
      • com.ibm.mq.explorer.ms0s.mqsceditor.gui.MQSCContentOutlinePage

  • public class MQSCContentOutlinePage
extends ContentOutlinePage

    This builds the contents of the Outline view. It registers a listener for MQSC Command events, which are emitted by the parser. But either better effort needs to be taken to ensure that the document isn't parsed multiple times or taken in this class to identify multiple events that are duplicates of each other.
